data.description: Welcome to the Luxury of Serenbe, Without The Price tag! This exquisite 3-level home tucked away in a serene cul-de-sac, where everyday living feels like a peaceful family staycation. This stunning property boasts 5 full bedrooms and 5 full baths, making it a dream for both entertaining and relaxing.    The home's charming Juliette open floor plan welcomes you with an extended length driveway leading to a side-entry garage and a spacious front porch. The brick/stone front appeal adds a touch of elegance to the exterior.     The first floor features a formal dining room and a living room with a cozy gas fireplace, perfect for gatherings. The spacious kitchen is a culinary enthusiast's delight, featuring granite countertops, a breathtaking breakfast bar island, and top of the line stainless steel appliances. Additionally, a guest bedroom/office with private bathroom access offers convenience and versatility.    Upstairs, a cozy loft area awaits, along with three bedrooms, each boasting its own private bathroom. The oversized owner's suite is a sunlit retreat with four windows offering spectacular views of the beautiful wooded backyard. The master suite also includes a sitting area and an en-suite bathroom featuring a spa-like, stone-tiled shower, a garden tub, a water closet, double vanity sinks with granite countertops, and a huge walk-in closet.    Now, let's talk about the basement, a key selling point of this home. This exclusive living space features a large family room, a private bedroom, a full bathroom, and a storage room, providing ample space for various activities and storage needs.It can be used for entertaining guests or as an in-law suite.    Moving outside, the backyard is a tranquil haven, highlighted by an impressive detached deck area set amidst a tree-lined grass lot. This deck area is perfect for relaxation, boasting a large jacuzzi, an incredible fire-pit, a built-in bench, string lighting, and ample space for patio furniture. Whether you seek a private romantic night or an evening of full entertainment, this 1/2-acre oasis is sure to exceed your expectations.    In addition to the detached deck, an attached deck just off the kitchen also offers a second jacuzzi, allowing you to unwind and enjoy the breathtaking views.    Conveniently located just minutes from I-85, 25 minutes from the airport, and only 30 minutes from downtown Atlanta, this best-kept secret is a truly exceptional find. Don't miss the opportunity to call this magnificent property yours!
